node.text:
You become what you constantly feed your mind with.

If you constantly feed your mind with, “I can’t afford that, I can’t be rich, I can’t do that...”

Well guess what, you’re right.

Instead of telling yourself statements, which only closes the mind.

Change it to: “HOW can I afford that?”, “How can I be rich?”, “How can I do that?”. 

This will broaden your mind and you will start to think of solutions to your problem rather than excuses.

Did you find this helpful? Follow @savetoinvest for more!

#robertkiyosaki #moneymindset #richmindset #richmind #mindsetshift #changeyourmindset #savetoinvest

node.text:
Before starting w/ any of these websites. Ask yourself what type of side hustle it is that you want to start.⁠
⁠
Is it a short-term side hustle to bring in some extra quick cash? ⁠
⁠
Or do you want to build an actual business, that you can grow & scale into something big? (This would involve making very little or no money at all when starting out.)⁠
⁠
If you want a short term side hustle, start with any of the freelancing websites: Fiverr.com, Upwork.com & Freelancer.com.⁠
⁠
If you want to build something for the long-term, I would recommend you start with a social media platform such as Instagram & Youtube.⁠
⁠
(Even TikTok is a great place to start, though it isn't listed in the post. Since it'll enable you to grow a following extremely quickly, and then you can use that momentum to grow your other social media channels.)⁠
⁠
